# Reflection â€” Workplace Etiquette (STAR)

**Situation:**  
During Term 2, I completed the Workplace Etiquette assessment, which tested my understanding of appropriate workplace behavior, professional communication, and conduct in different scenarios.

**Task:**  
My goal was to demonstrate professionalism and show that I could apply correct etiquette when handling confidential information, emails, meetings, and personal communication at work.

**Action:**  
I completed the online Workplace Etiquette quiz, carefully reading each scenario to select the most professional response. I focused on understanding how to remain respectful, punctual, and responsible in all work-related situations.

**Result:**  
I achieved full completion and improved my understanding of professional behavior in the workplace. I learned how to manage sensitive information, respond to conflict appropriately, and maintain a professional image in all work interactions.
